.同步调用</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-1-2-%E5%BC%82%E6%AD%A5%E9%80%9A%E7%9F%A5"><span class="toc-number">5.1.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.1.2.异步通知</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-1-3-%E7%9B%91%E5%90%ACbinlog"><span class="toc-number">5.1.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.1.3.监听binlog</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-1-4-%E9%80%89%E6%8B%A9"><span class="toc-number">5.1.4.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.1.4.选择</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-2-%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5"><span class="toc-number">5.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.2.实现数据同步</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-2-1-%E6%80%9D%E8%B7%AF"><span class="toc-number">5.2.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.2.1.思路</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-2-2-%E5%AF%BC%E5%85%A5demo"><span class="toc-number">5.2.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.2.2.导入demo</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#3-2-3-%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E6%9C%BA%E3%80%81%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97"><span class="toc-number">5.2.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">3.2.3.声明交换机、队列</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#1%EF%BC%89%E5%BC%95%E5%85%A5%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96"><span class="toc-number">5.2.3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">1）引入依赖</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#2%EF%BC%89%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E6%9C%BA%E5%90%8D%E7%A7%B0"><span class="toc-number">5.2.3.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">2）声明队列交换机名称</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#3%EF%BC%89%E5%A3%B0%E6%98%8E%E9%98%9F%E5%88%97%E4%BA%A4%E6%8D%A2%E6%9C%BA"><span class="toc-number"